did.unittitle: Short Run Student and University Publications
did.abstract: This collection contains old publications from The George Washington University offices and student groups that are no longer in publication. Most of these files only contain a few issues and are potentially incomplete runs. The publications range in date from 1884 to 2016.
did.physloc: Materials may be stored off-site, and may require additional retrieval time. Please contact the Special Collections Research Center for more information.

prefercite.head: Preferred citation
prefercite.p: Short Run Publications, Special Collections Research Center, The George Washington University.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: The collection was accessioned into the collection in 2001, but the provenance is unknown.

userestrict.head: Restrictions on Use
userestrict.p: Some material may be copyrighted or restricted. It is the patron's obligation to determine and satisfy copyright or other case restrictions when publishing or otherwise distributing materials found in the collections.

bioghist.head: Historical or Biographical Note
bioghist.p: A portion of this collection was part of a backlog that has an unknown provenance. In 2001, the items were accessioned into the collection within its own record group to contain University and student organization publications that are no longer published.

scopecontent.head: Collection Scope and Content
scopecontent.p: This collection contains publications from The George Washington University offices and student groups that are no longer being published. They range in date from 1884 to 2016. Most of these files only contain a few issues and are potentially incomplete runs.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: This series contains old publications from University offices and student groups that are no longer being published. They range in date from 1884 to 2005.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: This folder includes the newsletter, "GW Minute", which is produced by the Office of Government, International and Corporate Affairs. This publication primarily concerns community relations and involvement. This newsletter ranges in date from March 1999- September 2005.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: This folder includes the student run publication "GW Patriot", which is a monthly conservative journal that offers commentary on politics and culture at George Washington University. This newsletter ranges in date from March 2003- March 2005.
